platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Whether you’re simply looking for a new rug or planning a top-to-bottom room renovation, Houzz should be your first stop. It’s got a huge selection of furnishings, accessories, and lighting you can purchase with Apple Pay, but it's also full of photos to inspire your projects. A helpful community of users can lend a hand with suggestions, or you can connect with a contractor, designer, or landscaper right from the app to help make your home-improvement dream come true.
Get ideas from a huge selection of furnishings, accessories and lighting, inspirational photos and a helpful community to realise your home decor dreams.
透過各式各樣的傢俱、擺設、燈具選擇，以及大量的參考相片和樂於助人的社群獲取靈感，幫助你裝修出夢寐以求的理想家居。
Get ideas from a huge selection of furnishings, accessories, and lighting, inspirational photos and a helpful community to realize your home decor dreams.
你可以在這款 App 裡找到海量的家具、家飾與照明靈感，而且除了看照片之外，你還能和友善的社群互動，實現你的居家設計夢想。
Inspirez-vous d’une vaste sélection de meubles, d’accessoires et d’éclairages, de photos et d’une communauté d’entraide pour réaliser vos rêves de décoration.
